resources.string:
Would you like to be kept informed if you
have crossed paths with someone who has
tested COVID-19 positive?

Each one of us has the power to help
prevent the spread of the Corona Virus
pandemic in India.

This app tracks through a Bluetooth Location social graph,
your interaction with someone who could have tested
COVID-19 positive.

The App alerts are accompanied by 
instructions on how to self-isolate and what 
to do in case you develop symptoms that 
may need help and support

You will be alerted if you have come in close proximity
of someone, who has been tested COVID-19 positive.
With Aarogya Setu, you can protect yourself, \nyour family and friends, and help our \ncountry in the effort to fight COVID-19
